<div id="wrap">
<fieldset id="baseMetricGroup">
  <legend id="baseMetricGroup_Legend" title="Suatu karakteristik kelemahan yang spesifik dalam konteks operasional tertentu.">Environmental Score</legend>

 <div class="metric">
      <h3 id="BI_Heading" title="Menggambarkan dampak potensial terhadap bisnis atau misi jika kelemahan dapat berhasil dieksploitasi">Business Impact(BI)</h3>
      <input name="bim" value="C" id="BI_C" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_C" id="BI_C_Label" title="Bisnis/misi bisa gagal.">Critical (C)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="H" id="BI_H" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_H" id="BI_H_Label" title="Operasi bisnis/misi akan terpengaruh secara signifikan.">High (H)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="M" id="BI_M" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_M" id="BI_M_Label" title="Bisnis/misi akan terpengaruh, tetapi tanpa kerusakan yang luas untuk operasi rutin.">Medium (M)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="L" id="BI_L" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_L" id="BI_L_Label" title="Dampak minimal pada bisnis/misi.">Low (L)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="N" id="BI_N" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_N" id="BI_N_Label" title="Tidak ada dampak.">None (N)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="D" id="BI_D" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_D" id="BI_D_Label" title="The median of weights for Critical, High, Medium, Low, and None.">Default (D)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="UK" id="BI_UK" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_UK" id="BI_UK_Label" title="There is not enough information to provide a value for this factor. Further analysis may be necessary. In the future, a different value might be chosen, which could affect the score.">Unknown (UK)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="NA" id="BI_NA" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_NA" id="BI_NA_Label" title="This factor is being intentionally ignored in the score calculation because it is not relevant to how the scorer prioritizes weaknesses.
This factor might not be applicable in contexts in which the business impact is irrelevant, or if the impact is being assessed and considered in analytical processes that are outside of the CWSS score itself.">Not Applicable (NA)</label>
      <input name="bim" value="Q" id="BI_Q" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="BI_Q" id="BI_Q_Label" title="This factor could be quantified with custom weights. Some organizations might have specific measurements for the business value of the asset, for example, which could be integrated into this measurement.">Quantified (Q)</label>
    </div>


    <div class="metric">
      <h3 id="DI_Heading" title="Kemungkinan bahwa seorang penyerang dapat menemukan kelemahan">Likelihood Of Discovery(DI)</h3>
      <input name="di" value="H" id="DI_H" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_H" id="DI_H_Label" title="Sangat mungkin bahwa seorang penyerang dapat menemukan kelemahan dengan cepat dan dengan sedikit usaha menggunakan teknik sederhana, tanpa akses ke kode sumber atau artefak lain yang menyederhanakan deteksi kelemahan">High (H)</label>
      <input name="di" value="M" id="DI_M" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_M" id="DI_M_Label" title="Seorang penyerang mungkin dapat menemukan kelemahan, tetapi akan memerlukan keterampilan tertentu untuk melakukannya, mungkin memerlukan akses kode sumber atau pengetahuan reverse engineering">Medium (M)</label>
      <input name="di" value="L" id="DI_L" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_L" id="DI_L_Label" title="Seorang penyerang tidak mungkin untuk menemukan kelemahan tanpa keterampilan yang sangat khusus">Low (L)</label>
      <input name="di" value="D" id="DI_D" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_D" id="DI_D_Label" title="The median of the High, Medium, and Low values.">Default (D)</label>
      <input name="di" value="UK" id="DI_UK" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_UK" id="DI_UK_Label" title="There is not enough information to provide a value for this factor. Further analysis may be necessary. In the future, a different value might be chosen, which could affect the score.">Unknown (UK)</label>
      <input name="di" value="NA" id="DI_NA" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_NA" id="DI_NA_Label" title="This factor is being intentionally ignored in the score calculation because it is not relevant to how the scorer prioritizes weaknesses.
This might not be applicable when the scorer assumes that all weaknesses will be discovered by an attacker.">Not Applicable (NA)</label>
      <input name="di" value="Q" id="DI_Q" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="DI_Q" id="DI_Q_Label" title="This factor could be quantified with custom weights.">Quantified (Q)</label>
    </div>

<div class="metric">
      <h3 id="EX_Heading" title="Kemungkinan bahwa, jika kelemahan ditemukan, seorang penyerang dengan hak istimewa/otentikasi/akses yang diperlukan akan dapat berhasil mengeksploitasi itu.">Likelihood Of Exploit(EX)</h3>
      <input name="ex" value="H" id="EX_H" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_H" id="EX_H_Label" title="Sangat mungkin bahwa seorang penyerang akan menargetkan keberhasilan mengeksploitasi dengan mudah.">High (H)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="M" id="EX_M" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_M" id="EX_M_Label" title="Seorang penyerang mungkin akan menargetkan kelemahan ini berhasil, tetapi kemungkinan keberhasilan dapat bervariasi, atau memerlukan beberapa upaya untuk berhasil.">Medium (M)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="L" id="EX_L" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_L" id="EX_L_Label" title="Seorang penyerang mungkin tidak akan menargetkan kelemahan ini, atau bisa memiliki kemungkinan sangat terbatas pada keberhasilan.">Low (L)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="N" id="EX_N" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_N" id="EX_N_Label" title="Seorang penyerang tidak memiliki kesempatan untuk sukses; yaitu, masalahnya adalah bug karena tidak ada peran penyerang, dan tidak ada manfaat bagi penyerang. ">None (N)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="D" id="EX_D" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_D" id="EX_D_Label" title="Median of the High, Medium, and Low values. The None value is ignored with the expectation that few weakness findings would be scored using the value, and including it in the median calculation would reduce the weight to a non-intuitive level.">Default (D)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="UK" id="EX_UK" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_UK" id="EX_UK_Label" title="There is not enough information to provide a value for this factor. Further analysis may be necessary. In the future, a different value might be chosen, which could affect the score.">Unknown (UK)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="NA" id="EX_NA" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_NA" id="EX_NA_Label" title="This factor is being intentionally ignored in the score calculation because it is not relevant to how the scorer prioritizes weaknesses.
For example, the scorer might want to assume that attackers could exploit any weakness they can find, or be willing to invest significant resources to work around any possible barriers to exploit success.">Not Applicable (NA)</label>
      <input name="ex" value="Q" id="EX_Q" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EX_Q" id="EX_Q_Label" title="This factor could be quantified with custom weights.">Quantified (Q)</label>

     </div>

    <div class="metric">
      <h3 id="EC_Heading" title="Kemampuan kontrol atau Mitigations di luar perangkat lunak yang dapat membuat kelemahan lebih sulit bagi seorang penyerang untuk mencapai dan/atau memicu">Eksternal Control Effectiveness(EC)</h3>
      <input name="ec" value="N" id="EC_N" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_N" id="EC_N_Label" title="Tidak ada kontrol">None (N)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="L" id="EC_L" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_L" id="EC_L_Label" title="Ada metode sederhana atau pembatasan yang mungkin mencegah penyerang mengeksploitasi masalah">Limited (L)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="M" id="EC_M" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_M" id="EC_M_Label" title="Mekanisme perlindungan biasanya digunakan tetapi telah diketahui batasannya yang mungkin dilewati dengan beberapa upaya oleh penyerang berpengetahuan.">Moderate (M)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="I" id="EC_I" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_I" id="EC_I_Label" title="Kontrol tidak secara khusus melindungi terhadap eksploitasi kelemahan, tetapi secara tidak langsung mengurangi dampak ketika serangan berhasil diluncurkan, atau sebaliknya membuatnya lebih sulit untuk membangun eksploitasi fungsional.">Indirect (Defense in Dept) (I)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="B" id="EC_B" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_B" id="EC_B_Label" title="Kontrol terbaik saat ini, meskipun mungkin memiliki beberapa keterbatasan yang dapat diatasi oleh penyerang terampil">Best Available (B)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="C" id="EC_C" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_C" id="EC_C_Label" title="Kontrol sepenuhnya efektif terhadap kelemahan, yaitu, tidak ada bug atau kerentanan, dan tidak ada konsekuensi yang merugikan dari eksploitasi masalah.">Complete (C)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="D" id="EC_D" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_D" id="EC_D_Label" title="  
The median of Complete, Best-Available, Indirect, Moderate, Limited, and None.">Default (D)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="UK" id="EC_UK" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_UK" id="EC_UK_Label" title="There is not enough information to provide a value for this factor. Further analysis may be necessary. In the future, a different value might be chosen, which could affect the score.">Unknown (UK)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="NA" id="EC_NA" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_NA" id="EC_NA_Label" title="This factor is being intentionally ignored in the score calculation because it is not relevant to how the scorer prioritizes weaknesses">Not Applicable (NA)</label>
      <input name="ec" value="Q" id="EC_Q" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="EC_Q" id="EC_Q_Label" title="This factor could be quantified with custom weights.">Quantified (Q)</label>
   </div>

    <div class="metric">
      <h3 id="P_Heading" title="Seberapa sering jenis kelemahan ini muncul dalam perangkat lunak">Prevalence(P)</h3>
      <input name="p" value="W" id="P_W" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_W" id="P_W_Label" title="Kelemahan yang ditemukan di sebagian besar atau semua perangkat lunak dalam lingkungan terkait, dan mungkin terjadi beberapa kali dalam paket perangkat lunak yang sama.">Widespread (W)</label>
      <input name="p" value="H" id="P_H" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_H" id="P_H_Label" title="Kelemahan yang dihadapi sangat sering, tetapi tidak luas">High (H)</label>
      <input name="p" value="C" id="P_C" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_C" id="P_C_Label" title="Kelemahan yang dihadapi secara berkala">Common (C)</label>
      <input name="p" value="L" id="P_L" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_L" id="P_L_Label" title="Kelemahan yang dihadapi jarang, atau tidak pernah.">Limited (L)</label>
      <input name="p" value="D" id="P_D" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_D" id="P_D_Label" title="The median of Limited, Common, High, and Widespread.">Default (D)</label>
      <input name="p" value="UK" id="P_UK" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_UK" id="P_UK_Label" title="There is not enough information to provide a value for this factor. Further analysis may be necessary. In the future, a different value might be chosen, which could affect the score.">Unknown (UK)</label>
      <input name="p" value="NA" id="P_NA" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_NA" id="P_NA_Label" title="This factor is being intentionally ignored in the score calculation because it is not relevant to how the scorer prioritizes weaknesses.
When performing targeted scoring against specific weakness findings in an application, Prevalence is normally expected to be irrelevant, since the individual application and the analytical techniques determine how frequently the weakness occurs, and many aggregated scoring methods will generate larger scores if there are more weaknesses.">Not Applicable (NA)</label>
      <input name="p" value="Q" id="P_Q" type="radio"onclick="calculateTotal3()"><label for="P_Q" id="P_Q_Label" title="This factor could be quantified with custom weights. Precise prevalence data may be available within limited use cases, provided the user is tracking weakness data at a low level of granularity. For example, a developer may be tracking weaknesses across a suite of products, or a code-auditing vendor could measure prevalence from the software analyzed across the entire customer base. In a previous version of CWSS, prevalence was calculated based on from raw voting data that was collected for the 2010 Top 25, which used discrete values (range 1 to 4) which were then adjusted to a 1-to-10 range."> Quantified (Q)</label>
